videos.headline: Carter connects with James for 57-yd Norfolk State TD
videos.description: Juwan Carter runs the play action and connects with Da'Kendall James who traverses 57 yards to pay dirt for Norfolk State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Carter connects with James for 57-yd Norfolk State TD) 2019/08/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Norfolk State takes the lead on Carter's TD dash
videos.description: Juwan Carter jukes his way nine yards to the end zone to give Norfolk State a 21-17 lead over ODU in the fourth quarter.
